title: Yummy rye bread
ingredients: ['275ml water', '2 tablespoons black treacle', '1 tablespoon vegetable oil', '1 teaspoon salt', '250g plain flour', '155g rye flour', '3 tablespoons dark brown soft sugar', '1 tablespoon unsweetened cocoa powder', '3/4 teaspoon caraway seeds', '2 teaspoons easy bake yeast']
